snippet.title: Longplay of Batman: Rise of Sin Tzu
snippet.description:
Longplay of Batman: Rise of Sin Tzu, played as the NTSC version on the Game Boy Advance. This game's version was released on Oct. 27th, 2003. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

2:14:39 - boss: Sin Tzu
2:19:11 - ending

By: Reinc
